-- India to Ease Tourism Foreign Investment Rules, Financial Express Reports
-- Anil Varma
-- 2010-06-15T01:56:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/india-to-ease-tourism-foreign-investment-rules-financial-express-reports.html

          
          
             India plans to ease regulations for
foreign investment in hotels and tourism by waiving a three-year
lock-in period imposed on such holdings, the Financial Express
reported, without saying where it obtained the information.  
